  "course_notes": "(Same as CPLT 751R 4, PHIL 789 4, PSP 789 1) Topic: Marx, Lacan, Fanon: Feminist Formations Course Description: Marx, Lacan, Fanon Feminist formations (WGS 585): The seminar will examine questions of sexuality, gender, and race in the works of Marx, Lacan, and Fanon. It will also explore feminist debates within and across these discourses. In turn, it engages with concepts such as reproductive politics, economies, law, labor, and value.",
